717.1 The holder of an on-premises retailer&#8217;s license may permit a patrono bring to and consume on the licensed premises an alcoholic beverage that theicensee is permitted to sell or serve under its on-premises retailer&#8217;sicense;
      provided that the alcoholic beverage is opened by an employee of thestablishment, However, the holder of an on-premises retailer&#8217;s licensehall not permit any alcoholic beverage opened on the licensed premises to beemoved from the licensed
      premises.
